			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>One way to do this is like have a Super-Meditative state. To activate it one would, maybe, use one of the old vestiges of our spellbook.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Cast a spell similar to <A href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=2501&amp;source=Live" target=_blank>Sanctuary</A>, disallow PC's from triggering it. Have it broken upon standing after 2 ticks (also broken if you remain on a horse) so people have&nbsp;to sit down, have it broken upon detection of NPC in a 100 radius. From that point on have it cast a self only bardish mana regen tick, which could gain in strength every couple of ticks or so. With the trigger detection the song could be instantly broken as soon as a mob comes into range of your party.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Have the spell on a 5 minute recast so that people can't abuse it for long pulls, and I think this would be a workable suggestion for all classes.</DIV>
